aken together, our results detail the unique genetic and virological features of bat and rodent RVAs and demonstrate the need for further investigation of their zoonotic potential.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Kishimoto, Mai", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kajihara, Masahiro", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Tabata, Koshiro", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Itakura, Yukari", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Toba, Shinsuke", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ozono, Seiya", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sato, Yuko", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Suzuki, Tadaki", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ito, Naoto", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Changula, Katendi", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Qiu, Yongjin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mori-Kajihara, Akina", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Eto, Yoshiki", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Harima, Hayato", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mwizabi, Daniel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hang'ombe, Bernard M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hall, William W.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Takada, Ayato", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Orba, Yasuko", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sawa, Hirofumi", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sasaki, Michihito", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Parrish, Colin R.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/53cd9c81cdf6f1dc40b9970c084001fe", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/f8f693f101f01d5eca49113f9048b88cc1c4f76cde4a65759dd817d46a512123", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/RWQ8NS96", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/RWQ8NS96", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/471a47f4701f63b81a9b033486161d4a!/b96548